{"tid":1327513,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"同大家分享一樣兒時玩意，射乳膠漆廁紙","createTime":"2019-07-17T15:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T09:16:31.000Z","uid":154702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0f6ad43cd55795bd9881e31f4b128974c9851a","tid":1327513,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"細個好百厭，但係冇乜錢買玩具<br />\n所以好多自製野都係上網睇<br />\n<br />\n就好似以下呢一樣野咁樣<br />\n不過子彈由棉花糖改做<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>乳膠漆加廁紙</strong></span>做子彈<br />\n子彈大細大概係樽口既四份一<br />\n<br />\n記得嗰時屋村平台有好多閉路電視<br />\n我哋就係呢個黎打<br />\n成本低，又容易整<br />\n乳膠漆本身不會溶膠所以用得著<br />\n乾之前又可以用水洗，所以TK 都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過就要練下<br />\n同埋每次射完要洗返乾淨<br />\n乳膠漆乾咗會jam實個汽球<br />\n<br />\n幾高嘅閉路電視都打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時山上面有野狗跑落嚟咬我哋<br />\n我哋都係用呢個加油漆廁紙射到佢睇唔到嘢<br />\n<br />\n不過就唔建議用螺絲帽做子彈<br />\nTK真係會死得人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強烈建議大家奉公守法<br />\n香港嘅穩定繁榮得來不易<br />\n犯法野千祈唔好做</span><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家細個又點樣發揮創意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次冇開錯台，創意台啱晒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EYjv89fqeT4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEYjv89fqeT4&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=30d9a35a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EYjv89fqeT4</a>"},{"pid":"267df1e3d2b9e1a7c4ccb6c4a9695ef45c1c8e86","tid":1327513,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}